metadata.name: MetaPass Diamond Genesis #1
metadata.description: The 1st Edition of MetaJam Asia in Singapore, from 6 May - 31 July 2022. MetaPass Genesis holders are entitled to full event and summit access at MetaJam Asia 2022, and a series of perks and benefits such as whitelists, giveaways, NFT drops, exclusive IRL merchandise access and IRL perks with our partners.
metadata.creator: MetaJam Asia
